        "meta_description": "John Torode and his wife Lisa Faulkner have been married for three years after meeting on the set of Celebrity MasterChef, but the TV chef's road to true love was far from easy.",
        "meta_lang": "en",
        "meta_favicon": "https://s2-prod.dailyrecord.co.uk/@trinitymirrordigital/chameleon-branding/publications/dailyrecord/img/favicon.013e9710c3385915.ico",
